  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gwenview</title>

    <para>Gwenview is a fast and easy-to-use image viewer for KDE.</para>

    &lfs76_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
